    <text x="40" y="232" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Quarter ended Feb: $3.818B net loss (99% digital-asset revaluation)</text>
    <text x="40" y="254" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Early June, ETH below $1,800: unrealized loss up to $8.9B</text>
